Experimental next3 features:
----------------------------
- exclude files with 'nodump' flag (chattr +d) from snapshot

Unsupported ext3 features:
--------------------------
- user/group quotas (copy user/group quota blocks on snapshot take)
- direct I/O
- block size != PAGE_SIZE
- data journaling

Stability
--------------------
- unit testing of post crash recovery

Performance:
------------
- run file system benchmarks
- improved block allocation strategies for snapshot file
- use single page for unmodified blocks (via special snapshot loop device)

